Package com.easylease.easylease.model.order

Domain classes used for Order.

These classes contain the order model and the operations that can be performed by Data Access Object (DAO) that accesses objects of type Order.

Since:
0.1
Version:
0.2
Author:
Antonio Sarro
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    OrderDao
    Interface that provides the operations that can be performed on the DataBase for the Order Object.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    DbOrderDao
    This class implements the OrderDAO interface, using the singleton DBConnection as the database.
    DbOrderDaoTest
    Test of the DBOrderDAO model.
    Order
    This class models an object of type Order within the system.
    OrderTest
    Test of the Order model.
